oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Ellis, Bob; Hussiein, Anmon; Ratamyus; Austin, Norvell; Mills, Doug; Hollywood Blondes (wrestling group); Wrestling
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Handwritten notes for an order of posters featuring Phillips Community College wresting matches between Hollywood Blondes vs. Bill Dundee and Cowboy Bob Ellis, Anmon Hussiein vs Ratamyus, and Norvell Austin vs. Doug Mills on Thursday, July 14. Posters were ordered by Buddy Wayne.
